# Cloudflare Pages redirects.
# True HTTP 301 for /github → framework repo (PRD §3 / §9). This takes
# precedence over the Astro-generated /github/index.html meta-refresh page,
# which stays as a fallback for any other host. Keep in sync with the
# `redirects` entry in astro.config.mjs.
/github  https://github.com/open-multi-agent/open-multi-agent  301

# Historical product URL still linked from third-party sites. Preserve its
